{
  "texts": [
    "Participant insights presented balanced perspectives on the use of ChatGPT for academic purposes, highlighting both its strengths and weaknesses.",
    "One of the key issues raised was the simplicity of the generated content.",
    "Whilst simplicity holds merit in specific contexts, particularly in academic writing at the master level, it can signify a lack of depth or sophistication, potentially undermining the complexity required for success at this level.",
    "Another limitation identified was the repetition of the content.",
    "Repetitive arguments or statements can significantly undermine the impact of an essay, as they can suggest a lack of comprehensive research or insufficient engagement with the subject matter."
  ]
}